{"tid":2168533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我真係好愛你架 但..","createTime":"2020-08-21T21:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T14:06:12.000Z","uid":271444,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4dcbc7488f46a44a64489126062bec5a10a6c98","tid":2168533,"uid":271444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"只不過你終於離開左我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得初初係隻online game到識你<br />\n你會主動搵我傾計，一齊玩<br />\n漸漸咁比你吸引，再到鍾意你，真係好快<br />\n<br />\n慢慢地..關係逐漸疏遠<br />\n其實我都感受到架.. 但我邊有資格要求咁多<br />\n<br />\n你嫌我成日將啲嘢由佢<br />\n因為我總係選擇去逃避唔如意嘅事<br />\n我唔開心亦都唔會同你講，將啲野收埋收埋<br />\n所以令你覺得你唔夠重要，覺得我唔信你<br />\n但其實我真係甚少同人表露自己唔開心嘅一面<br />\n做咩之前我都諗過度過 因為我怕令你唔開心<br />\n但原來咁樣先係令你最唔開心嘅原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依幾日一直掙扎好唔好搵返你<br />\n但我知自己真係好難改到個濕鳩性格<br />\n就算你接受，好彩氹返你<br />\n不久之後都會再係咁<br />\n所以...對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我真係好愛你...好想每晚都有你陪住我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5c09e4f1352c6dc059172cf8baf274b3f0a26f","tid":2168533,"uid":308450,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T21:21:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1341b83ec74ebdc4106c9291649adcb6774c7151","tid":2168533,"uid":271444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T21:23:06.000Z","msg":"sorry...打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日先岩.."},{"pid":"95f29ae18481991141e5d798a8800c5bca9fa796","tid":2168533,"uid":156818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T21:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />bro"},{"pid":"e73b7edf690d955c993b29fb2f8ae74866d7fbee","tid":2168533,"uid":271444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-